3658,東海課程-第二外國語德文（二）(Manfred Sablotny(夏慕帆)老師1132-3658) ,Manfred Sablotny,選修課,0-3,"二/6,7四/6","全球約有1.19億人說德語，它也是1.01億歐洲人的母語。因此德語是歐洲使用最廣的語言，其使用率在全球排名第十。會講德語能有很多機會豐富自己的人生和增進對歐洲文化特色的認識。此外德語在研究與學術方面也是全球第二重要的語言。本課程的目標有：
* basic training in pronunciation and intonation 
* building basic listening and reading comprehension
* strengthening (language) learning skills
* enabling students to express themselves in simple sentences and paragraphs in oral and written form by training understanding of sentence structures, grammar, vocabulary, sentence patterns in relation to particular situations
* providing background in regional / cultural studies
* strengthening interaction between students and developing collaborative skills working alone, with a partner and in groups
* enacting dialogues of everyday situations
* listening to native speakers and working with material typical of the target culture
* collecting relevant language and culture information"
3659,東海課程-第二外國語德文（四）(游曉嵐老師1132-3659) ,游曉嵐,選修課,0-3,LAN012,"全球約有1.19億人說德語，它也是1.01億歐洲人的母語。因此德語是歐洲使用最廣的語言，其使用率在全球排名第十。會講德語能有很多機會豐富自己的人生和增進對歐洲文化特色的認識。此外德語在研究與學術方面也是全球第二重要的語言。本課程的目標有：
- basic training in pronunciation and intonation 
- building basic listening and reading comprehension
- enabling students to express themselves in simple sentences and paragraphs in oral and written form by training understanding of sentence structures, grammar, vocabulary, sentence patterns in relation to particular situations
- providing background in regional / cultural studies
- strengthening interaction between students and developing collaborative skillsworking alone, with a partner and in groups; enacting dialogues of everyday situations; dialogue variations; listening to native speakers; working with material typical of the target culture; collecting relevant language and culture information; doing independent online research"
3660,東海課程-第二外國語法文（一）(Rémy Mettetal老師1132-3660) ,Rémy Mettetal,選修課,0-3,AG104,"1.透過自然發音法讓學生掌握法語基本發音和語調,使其自然開口說法語.
2.藉由教材生動的對話,深入淺出循序漸進,學習各種基礎文法,字彙,句型和實用會話,以達到法語鑑定DELF A1為目標,奠定法語聽說
讀寫的基本能力.
3.營造輕鬆自然學習語文的氛圍,著重課堂上的互動,以溝通式教學法,配合各式補充教材的情境,讓學生更熟悉法文語法邏輯,輕鬆開口說法文.
4.透過語言拓展視野,認識法國文化,讓語言和實際生活和工作能結合運用."
3661,東海課程-第二外國語法文（二）(蔡明華老師1132-3661) ,蔡明華,選修課,0-3,LAN014,"Teaching outline
