4081,東海課程-大二英文大二英文：職涯與專業(閔譯平老師1132-4081) ,閔譯平,必修課,0-2,LAN005,"[主題: 給初學者的職場英語課]
這門課程的目標是幫助學生掌握在職場環境中所需的基本聽說讀寫技能，讓他們能夠用英文與同事和客戶進行溝通。這個課程沒有紙筆測驗，而是讓同學們以完成各項作業或課後任務的分數為主。期中和期末成績的部分，將包括撰寫英文履歷和錄製求職自我介紹的影片。除此之外，大家也有機會在課程中和同學及老師用英文對話、互動。學生需使用英文錄影音檔案來完成課堂或課後作業。

[Course: Working English for Beginners]
The aim of this course is to prepare students with the fundamental four skills they need to work in an environment in which they required to communicate with both their colleagues and customers in English. Rather than traditional quizzes, students' grades will be based on their participation and completion of various in-class and after-class assignments. Both midterm and final assessments will involve writing an English resume and making a self-introduction video for a job application. Additionally, the course will offer opportunities for students to engage in English conversations with their classmates and the instructor. Students will also be required to submit audio and video recordings as part of their in-class and homework assignments."
4082,東海課程-大二英文大二英文：職涯與專業(白浩廷老師1132-4082) ,白浩廷,必修課,0-2,LAN014,"Sophomore English: Career and Professional
Subtitle: A jump start to master business English

In this course, students will be trained to acquire the English skills needed in the workplace. Various activities in English listening, speaking, reading, and writing will be provided. After taking this course, Students will learn the interactive skills, the cultures, and the expectations in the workplace. They will also grow the abilities to use English to conduct an interview, compose a cover letter, and edit a resume of their own.

大二英文: 職涯與專業
副標題: 職場英文先修班 

增進職場英文能力是本課程的訓練目標, 課程中將提供多種英文聽說讀寫的訓練活動.
修畢本課程, 學生們將會學到職場互動技巧, 職場文化與期待,並有能力完成英文面試, 撰寫英文履歷表與工作申請信."
4083,東海課程-大二英文大二英文：日常溝通(陳永豪老師1132-4083) ,陳永豪,必修課,0-2,LAN011,"【英語玩家】
喜歡玩遊戲嗎？可曾想過人活著就像是在玩一場史詩級的角色扮演遊戲呢？想要玩好名為「人生」的遊戲需要好幾項技能，語言是其中一項。能多說一種除了母語以外的語言就能無限強化自己在這個遊戲裡的角色，只要想學，隨時都可以開始。在這門課裡，大家都是「英語」玩家。玩家們可以透過另一種語言看世界，吸收、討論、呈現關於這個世界的種種，玩透這世界。一起以駕馭英語為目標邁進吧！

[English Player One]
Do you like games? Have you ever thought that this life you are living right now is a huge RPG world? It actually is! One of the ways to get the most out of this game/world/life is to equip yourself with another language. Being able to speak another language other than your mother tongue is an ability, a skill, a talent, and, for some people, even a blessing. However, learning a new language is always possible as long as you make up your mind to start. So, in this course, you will use the English language to learn more about how you, as an \"English\" player, can see the world from a different point of view and have more fun living in it."
4084,東海課程-大二英文大二英文：日常溝通(Daniel Cothran老師1132-4084) ,Daniel Cothran,必修課,0-2,LAN015,"Communicating With People from Western Cultures英語通四海

This course aims to give students the language tools to communicate more effectively and comfortably in English with Westerners. Students will learn common expressions when talking about daily topics and discuss how culture plays an important role in choosing what and what not to talk about. Short reading and listening passages will introduce a topic and give students material to begin conversations. 

本課程的目標是為了提供語言工具，讓學生得以更有效更自在地使用英文和西方人士溝通。學生將學習到如何以常用語彙談論日常話題，以及在選定話題時文化所扮演的重要角色。短篇閱讀和聽力訓練也提供給學生一些對話的主題和素材."
4085,東海課程-大二英文大二英文：多元文化(郭俊銘老師1132-4085) ,郭俊銘,必修課,0-2,LAN013-1,"On completion of the course, students should be able to:
1. have enlarged their vocabulary and improved their listening comprehension;
2. communicate with people using more useful phrases and expressions;
3. read various materials in everyday life with better understanding;
4. improve communicative grammar skills and knowledge of of word parts; and
5. have become independent thinkers through activities that require critical thinking.reading/translation exercises, group discussion and presentation, quizzes, exams, etc."
4086,東海課程-大二英文大二英文：多元文化(李孟螢老師1132-4086) ,李孟螢,必修課,0-2,LAN208,"當代全球議題
本課程旨在讓學生在探討當今世界面臨的挑戰之餘，提升英文溝通能力並培養批判性思考技能。學生將在課堂中針對永續發展目標的相關議題搜尋資料、分享結果，並表達個人觀點；此外，學生也會實際參與服務學習或議題實踐活動，獲得體驗學習和自我反思的機會。

Contemporary Global Issues
This course is designed for students who wish to enhance their communicative proficiency in English and develop critical thinking skills while exploring the challenges our world faces today. Students will have opportunities to conduct in-class research on issues related to Sustainable Development Goals (SDGs), present their findings, and express their opinions. Additionally, they will engage in activities that offer experiential learning and self-reflection, such as service-learning projects or hands-on activities addressing issues discussed in class."
4087,東海課程-大二英文大二英文：自我表達技巧(朱先仙老師1132-4087) ,朱先仙,必修課,0-2,LAN210,"課程目標及內涵 (Course Objectives and Contents)
This course aims to engage the learners’ interest by different topics and use the language to do the presentation.
In this course there will be presentation skills, communication skills which based on different topics which can help pupils plan their career planning and development and also expand their worldview.
The presentation skills will be practicing a lot during the course. And the students will have lots opportunities to do the presentation on different topics.
After the course pupils can communicate more efficient and more confident in English in different topics. 
這門課主要讓學生以不同的主題來練習簡報技巧。
所以在這門課簡報技巧溝通技巧都會充分的被練習到可以讓學生預備他們的職涯生涯技能，不同主題的分享及探討也可以擴展他們的世界觀。
學生們會有很多機會來練習這些技巧根據不同的主題，在此課程也可以練習到很多溝通技巧以及各種不同領域的溝通方式跟字␀␀。"
4088,東海課程-大二英文大二英文：職涯與專業(蔡妮燕老師1132-4088) ,蔡妮燕,必修課,0-2,LAN015-1,"【主題:職涯規劃超前部署】:
本課程針對學生在未來職場，特別是英語工作環境中須具備之能力預作規劃與準備。每堂課除了配合教材之各種主題加強同學聽說讀寫等相關英語能力之外，同時也教導學生基礎求職及專業職場的英語技能，例如：如何適當撰寫求職信和履歷表，會議簡報，及運用策略做出有效溝通等，期望修完課的每位同學都能在邁入全球職場前獲得重要且實用之職涯專業知識與技能。

[Theme of this course: English for career development]:
The course is expected to prepare students for working in an English-speaking job environment. All four English skills—reading, listening, speaking and writing—are to be taught and enhanced in each unit. Essential professional English skills are included as well, such as giving presentations, participating in meetings and negotiating, job hunting and interviews, writing resumes, etc. It is hoped that the course will provide students with the essential tools for working in a globalized world."
4089,東海課程-大二英文大二英文：職涯與專業(林靜美老師1132-4089) ,林靜美,必修課,0-2,LAN014-1,"「職涯規劃超前佈署」
本課程提供職場所需的語言技巧與知識，以有效促進學生英文溝通能力，讓學習者在職場的英語能力表現更上一層樓。


 「English for Career Development」

Offering activities based on the real workplace and everyday communication at work for students"
4090,東海課程-大二英文大二英文：日常溝通(Henry Westheim老師1132-4090) ,Henry Westheim,必修課,0-2,LAN010,"Everyday English (日常英語)

This course is designed for students who want to improve their fluency, accuracy and confidence using English in informal daily conversations.

The primary focus is on listening, speaking, and conversation. Students will have numerous opportunities to speak English in the class. Through small group and class-wide discussions, their listening comprehension will be strengthened. Students will express ideas, opinions, and connect personal experiences and knowledge to daily topics. In addition, reading and listening materials will aid students in critical thinking and help them develop organizing of ideas and reasoning skills."
